---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/band/PageHero.astro';
import FeatureRow from '../../components/band/FeatureRow.astro';
import OverlayFeature from '../../components/band/OverlayFeature.astro';
import CtaBand from '../../components/band/CtaBand.astro';
import { SITE } from '../../lib/site';

const traits = [
  { title: 'Strong prayer life', desc: 'Everything begins on the knees. Leaders are formed in prayer before they are ever sent out.' },
  { title: 'Humble dependency and submission to God', desc: 'Reliance on God rather than self, following His direction over their own ambition.' },
  { title: 'Passion for the Kingdom mission', desc: 'A burning desire to see God’s Kingdom advance among their own people and beyond.' },
  { title: 'Focused study of God’s Word', desc: 'Grounded in Scripture, so they can teach and disciple others faithfully.' },
  { title: 'Discipleship', desc: 'Leaders who make leaders, multiplying themselves into the next generation.' },
  { title: 'Desire to serve native to their location', desc: 'A heart to reach their own tribe, language, and region first.' },
  { title: 'Developed vision, calling, and gifts from God', desc: 'Clarity about how God has uniquely equipped them, and the courage to walk in it.' },
];
---
<PageLayout
  title="Mission & Vision"
  description="The verbatim mission, vision, and founding convictions of Favor International."
>
  <PageHero
    label="Mission & Vision"
    title="Transformed Hearts Transform Nations"
    promise="Favor International serves and trains indigenous African leaders to advance the Gospel into the unreached."
    image="/images/hero-prayer-recent.jpg"
    imageAlt="A Favor prayer gathering"
  />

  <section class="band band--cream">
    <div class="container container--narrow mv-vision">
      <p class="label">Our vision</p>
      <p class="vision">{SITE.vision}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="band band--cream mv-mission">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <p class="label">Our mission</p>
      <p class="mission-body">{SITE.mission}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <OverlayFeature
    image="/images/hero-new-believers.jpg"
    imageAlt="New believers gathered in the field"
    eyebrow="Why we exist"
    heading="A spiritual army from the broken, lost, and impoverished."
    side="left"
  >
    <p>
      God has raised Favor up to mobilize a spiritual army from the broken, lost, and
      impoverished in 10+ countries. This army will raise up the next generation of soldiers
      growing and expanding the Kingdom of God that will overcome the strongholds of darkness
      that have long plagued Northern Africa.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Favor International serves to transform war-torn victims into purpose-driven
      Christian victors</strong>, equipped to advance the Gospel in villages and mobilized to
      advance the Kingdom in nations.
    </p>
    <p>
      We see trauma resolved, communities revitalized, at-risk children rescued from
      traffickers, poverty shrinking, and darkness driven away by the power of the Gospel in
      action.
    </p>
  </OverlayFeature>

  <FeatureRow
    image="/images/about-leadership-training.jpg"
    imageAlt="A Favor leadership training session"
    eyebrow="How we do it"
    heading="National leaders, on the front lines."
    layout="image-right"
    background="cream"
  >
    <p class="lede">
      Our passion is to mobilize national leaders in front-line battlegrounds to align their
      communities with the purposes of God in every aspect of life.
    </p>
    <p>
      National leaders are solving problems others haven't been able to. They are willing to
      work harder, more self-sacrificially, and more effectively for their people and nation
      than we ever could. Our work is to serve and train them and ensure they have everything
      they need to multiply and accelerate individual and national transformation. National
      leadership is one of our core principles in Favor.
    </p>
  </FeatureRow>

  <section class="band band--cream mv-traits">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <h2>What we instill in the leaders we train</h2>
      <ul class="trait-list">
        {traits.map((t) => (
          <li><strong class="trait-list__title">{t.title}</strong><span class="trait-list__desc">{t.desc}</span></li>
        ))}
      </ul>
      <p class="mv-sow">
        Transformation takes time and commitment. Investing in national leadership and
        discipleship has proven to be the most fruitful way to administer transformation. Our
        ministry is committed to not just give temporary relief and then leave. We are here to
        sow for a lifetime.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <OverlayFeature
    image="/images/evangelism-discipleship.jpg"
    imageAlt="Indigenous evangelism and discipleship in the field"
    eyebrow="The Gospel comes first"
    heading="The Gospel goes first, then everything follows."
    side="right"
  >
    <p>
      <strong>Favor gets the Gospel out to unreached areas where few others go, and we lead
      discipleship efforts beyond mere evangelism to produce fruit that multiplies.</strong>
    </p>
    <p>
      The Gospel is foundational to all other humanitarian work (education, orphanages,
      business, medical, etc.) and must be in place for other organizations to effectively do
      their work. National leaders can better access all spheres of their societies with
      greater speed and less expense than western missionaries.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Favor's vision is to see national leaders of all walks of life, equipped by the
      rest of the body of Christ, establish national leaders of all walks of life to disciple
      other national leaders, to further establish the Kingdom of God.</strong>
    </p>
  </OverlayFeature>

  <CtaBand
    heading="Stand with the mission."
    body="Becoming a Favor Partner is the simplest way to put this mission into motion every month."
    ctaLabel="Become a Favor Partner"
    ctaHref="/give/partner-monthly/"
  />
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .mv-vision { text-align: center; }
  .vision {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4.8vw, 3.6rem);
    color: var(--color-green-deep);
    margin: var(--space-3) 0 0;
    line-height: 1.12;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }
  .mv-mission { padding-top: 0; }
  .mission-body {
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 1.6vw, 1.4rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 760px;
  }
  .lede {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-gold-light);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .mv-sow { margin-top: var(--space-8); max-width: 640px; }
  .trait-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: var(--space-6) 0 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--space-4); }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .trait-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .trait-list li {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px;
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-6);
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-left: 5px solid var(--accent, var(--color-gold));
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  }
  .trait-list__title { color: var(--color-green); font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.02rem; line-height: 1.25; }
  .trait-list__desc { color: var(--color-ink-soft); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.5; }
  .trait-list li:nth-child(4n+1) { --accent: var(--color-gold-deep); }
  .trait-list li:nth-child(4n+2) { --accent: var(--color-green-bright); }
  .trait-list li:nth-child(4n+3) { --accent: var(--color-terracotta); }
  .trait-list li:nth-child(4n+4) { --accent: var(--color-sage); }
</style>
